<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  {% include 'head.njk' %} {% block head %} {% endblock %}
</head>
<body>
  <main class="mainGrid page">
    {% include 'header.njk' %} {% include 'nav.njk' %} {% include
    'toc.njk' %}
    <article class="gridBody">
      <div class="content">
        {% block main %}
        <h2>Introduction</h2>Hi, I'm <a href="https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2393-8056
">Rohit Goswami</a>. I'm a senior
        project associate at IIT Kanpur, where I work in the
        <a href=
        "https://femtolab.science/people/rohit">FemtoLab</a> under
        the stellar <a href=
        "https://femtolab.science/people/guide">Prof. Debabrata
        Goswami</a>. I post details of some of my projects
        sporadically, along with some thoughts on subjects I have taken. Elsewhere on the web, I'm better known by
        handle, `HaoZeke`. My sporadically updated CV may be
        <a href=
        "https://github.com/HaoZeke/CV/blob/master/RG_Latest-cv.pdf">
          found here</a>, and my <a href="dotdoom.grimoire.science">emacs-config is here</a>.
        <h3>Structure</h3>The site is divided into a multitude of
        collections and tags, accessible from the left navbar and
        from within posts.
        <h3>Rationale</h3>Each collection represents a coherent
        subject wise layout, while tags are meant to showcase the
        interdisciplinary aspects of each post.
        <ul class="catList">
          {% for name,data in collections | dictsort %}
          <h3 class="category">{{ name | replace('-', ' ') | capitalize }}</h3>{%
          for page in data %}
          <li>
            <strong>
            <a href="{{rootPath}}/{{page.path}}/index.html" title=
            "{{page.title}}">{{page.title}}</a> 
            </strong>
            <!-- <code>{{page.date}}</code> -->
            <div class="catBlurb">
              {{ page.blurb }}
            </div>
          </li>{% endfor %} {% endfor %}
        </ul>{% endblock %}
      </div>
    </article>{% include 'footer.njk' %}
  </main>{% block scripts %} {% endblock %}
  <script src="{{rootPath}}js/bundle.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
